tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE WeatherData (
  date TIMESTAMP,
  temperature FLOAT,
  humidity FLOAT,
  wind_speed FLOAT,
  solar_radiation FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE GridOperations (
    operation_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    operation_type VARCHAR(50),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE weather_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    temperature FLOAT,
    humidity FLOAT,
    wind_speed FLOAT,
    precipitation FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE solar_power_generation (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    power_generation FLOAT,
    efficiency FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE grid_operations (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    operation_id INT,
    operation_type VARCHAR(100),
    operation_status VARCHAR(50),
    operation_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE prediction_results (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    predicted_power_generation FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    event_description TEXT
)
